snippet.title: ITORAH | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Dive into the world of Nahucan, a fantastic place inhabited by strangely masked beings.
Guide Itorah, seemingly the only human left, and help her to face the challenge to save this wonderful world from it's biggest threat, the black plague. #ITORAH on Steam:








   

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1132910/ITORAH/
